<br>
You can really use Shock of lightning effectively. A bard with great gear will be difficult, but you can take a warrior down without a fungi pretty steadily with SoL and a lev. <br>
<br>
I beat a 51 DE warrior, and a 54 Troll Warrior both in Kael, both at the same time at level 48 - How?<br>
<br>
I levved up, waited until they were finished with their fight (51 warrior at 60% health) and nuked him. He turned around looking for me, and nuked him again (boh with conflag). I needed a little bit of flurry so I Elnerick's Entomement of Iced him. Didn't land, and he was getting close - both started laying some smack down on me, and I  levitated off one of the cliffs (we were on EW side, just a little out form the zone in). <br>
<br>
Eventually, I got the DE warrior to fall and lay unconcious while I managed to get a quick Shock of lightning on him right after. Looted his corpse while the Troll hacked me once. <br>
<br>
I headed over (and right next) to the blank giants spawn spots (They'd just killed earlier) and egged the troll on some. One nuke of Conflag and he was down to 75%. I was low on Mana and wasn't sure how things woudl turn out, so I headed back up to the cliffs I knocked the DE warrior down from, got some altitude, and hovered off (Troll watching to see what I was going to do) and gated out. <br>
<br>
I didn't get both, but I got the one, and thats what wizies do- We're the cheetah, We take things down quick.<br>
<br>
